A '''Banana''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] produced each day by a [[Banana Tree]] during its harvest season. A banana tree on the [[The Farm|farm]] in Stardew Valley produces fruit during [[Summer]]. On [[Ginger Island]] or in the [[Greenhouse]], it produces fruit year-round.

A [[Blue Discus]] [[Fish Pond]] has a 5-15% chance of producing a banana daily once the population of the pond reaches 4.

