==Tailoring==
Banana is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a dyeable {{name|Relaxed Fit Pants|link=Tailoring#Pants{{!}}Relaxed Fit Pants|class=inline}}. It is a yellow dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the yellow dye pot at [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]], for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
Banana is not used in any [[quests]].

==Golden Walnuts==
Banana is used to activate the Banana Shrine on [[Ginger Island#Island East|Ginger Island]], to the left of the staircase leading to [[Leo]]'s house.  When a banana is placed on the shrine the torches light and a gorilla appears and gives the player 3 [[Golden Walnut]]s.

